data.description: This lovely vintage home still has its original hard wood floors! Large bedrooms with extra natural lighting in the master. 2 bathrooms, ample living area with a wood burning fireplace for those cool days on their way. Kitchen has an open living/dining area with an office nook! Lower level includes separate entrance, 2 bedroom options, a full bath and small bonus space and a laundry sink. The one car garage with entrance to home and the large  fully fenced yard makes this very accommodating for big family BBQ's or parties.  Centrally located for convenient grocery shopping or enjoying the city park. Call me or your favorite agent to see today.
